data.description: Experience the epitome of urban living in this sophisticated downtown loft! Revel in its modern design situated in the sought-after ICON building at the center of the vibrant East Village. Only 26 minimum day rental per HOA and great opportunity! This upgraded and move-in-ready space boasts smart home features such as Bluetooth lighting and a Nest system. With 13-foot ceilings and floor-to-ceiling windows, bask in an abundance of natural light without compromising privacy. Indulge in designer carpet, chic cement light fixtures, stylish wood flooring, and an overall abundance of contemporary flair. Embrace the fusion of contemporary style with historical charm featuring Vintage Carnation Dairy windows dating back to the 1920s factory era. Revel in the soaring ceilings that encapsulate an ambiance of spaciousness. Experience the industrial design with concrete walls, exposed ducts, and stainless steel appliances, showcasing a perfect blend of modernity and historical character. Plus, enjoy the convenience of a large storage unit and parking space close to elevator. ICON offers an array of premium amenities including round-the-clock, year-round security, an exclusive rooftop deck with BBQ grills that boast direct views of the City, Ocean/Bay, Coronado Bridge and Petco Park plus a fully-equipped fitness center, a private movie theater and a clubhouse. Conveniently situated for effortless access to restaurants, nightlife, public transportation and more! Everything you desire is within easy walking distance. VA and FHA approved! This is a must see!
